      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:48:1",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) عَنِ التَّعْزِيرِ كَمْ هُوَ قَالَ بِضْعَةَ عَشَرَ سَوْطاً مَا بَيْنَ الْعَشَرَةِ إِلَى الْعِشْرِينَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Abu Ali Al Ashary, from Muhammad Bin Abdul Jabbar, from Safwan Bin Yahya, from Is’haq Bin Ammar who said, ",
          "‘I asked Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> about the reprimanding, how much is it?’ He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘A part of (about) ten lashes, what is between the ten to the twenty’."
        ]
      }
    }
